        </div>

        <h3>Changes to the privacy statement</h3>
        <p>This privacy statement can be amended to continue to comply with applicable regulations.</p>
        <p>If this privacy statement is amended, this will be reported on the Dodona
          <a href="https://docs.dodona.be/en/news/">news page</a>, with a reference to the amended privacy statement in the relevant
          news item. A reference to the most recent version of the privacy statement can always be found in the Dodona
          footer.</p>
